  "status": "success",
  "message": "New User Details Has been added",
  "data": {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Akash Jena",
    "email": "akash@gmail.com",
    "phone": "9876543210"
  }
}


Errors:

UserExistByEmailException ‚Üí email already exists

400 Bad Request ‚Üí validation fails

b) Edit User

Request Body:

{
  "name": "Akash Jena",
  "email": "newakash@gmail.com",
  "phone": "9876543210"
}


Response:

{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "User Details has been updated",
  "data": {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Akash Jena",
    "email": "newakash@gmail.com",
    "phone": "9876543210"
  }
}


